name: World of Warships: Legends - Liberty pack 2020
name_original: World of Warships: Legends - Liberty pack 2020
description:
It’s time to overpower your enemies!

Gain the upper hand against your opponents with a Liberty Pack. Increase your in-game achievements with a stack of additional supplies, including boosters, camouflages, and Premium Account time.

This bundle includes: - 4 days of Premium Account - 7x Type 4 camouflages - 7x rare boosters of naval expertise - 7x rare credits boosters - 7x rare boosters of commander expertise - 7x rare boosters of general expertise - 7x rare boosters of battle propensity
